<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 22:07:52 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国众议院通过有争议的法案，迫使拜登向以色列运送已暂停的炸弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-contentious-bill-forcing-biden-to-deliver-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel/0000018f-8315-d7f9-a5ff-b77790f90000</link><description>白宫已经表示，如果这项“极其不严肃”的法案提交总统办公桌，它将予以否决</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 21:14:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-house-passes-contentious-bill-forcing-biden-to-deliver-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel/0000018f-8315-d7f9-a5ff-b77790f90000</guid></item><item><title>“为阻止阿拉伯接管而感到自豪”：以色列的斯莫特里奇证实《纽约时报》的调查，称其为“血腥诽谤”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/proud-to-prevent-arab-takeover-smotrich-confirms-nyt-investigation-dubs-it-blood-libel/0000018f-82c9-d430-a38f-c7ed60800000</link><description>斯莫特里奇在回应一份已发布的文件时写道：“我很自豪能够战斗并阻止阿拉伯人占领这些领土，并帮助定居西岸的犹太英雄合法化。该文件指责他破坏了取缔非法定居点建设的努力。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:23:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/proud-to-prevent-arab-takeover-smotrich-confirms-nyt-investigation-dubs-it-blood-libel/0000018f-82c9-d430-a38f-c7ed60800000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡政府告诉高等法院，计划推进甘茨的正统法案草案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-tells-high-court-it-plans-to-advance-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill/0000018f-82d2-d430-a38f-c7f619650000</link><description>以色列总检察长表示，议员本尼·甘茨提交并经上届政府一读批准的征兵法不适合该国目前的安全形势。尽管如此，政府部长们表示他们计划在七月底之前批准该法案</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:19:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-government-tells-high-court-it-plans-to-advance-gantzs-haredi-draft-bill/0000018f-82d2-d430-a38f-c7f619650000</guid></item><item><title>加拿大因约旦河西岸暴力事件对四名以色列人实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/canada-sanctions-four-israelis-over-west-bank-violence/0000018f-82ed-d720-a79f-abff122f0000</link><description>加拿大效仿美国和英国的类似措施，针对被指控对巴勒斯坦人及其财产实施暴力的四名个人，并禁止他们进入加拿大</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 20:13:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/canada-sanctions-four-israelis-over-west-bank-violence/0000018f-82ed-d720-a79f-abff122f0000</guid></item><item><title>即使给以色列带来灾难，内塔尼亚胡和他的伙伴也不会停止</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-partners-will-not-stop-even-after-bringing-disaster-upon-israel/0000018f-82a5-d430-a38f-c7e51d600000</link><description>战争的延长、总理在国内外的软弱以及以色列正在成为贱民国家的事实只会加剧内塔尼亚胡的救世主情结</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:36:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-partners-will-not-stop-even-after-bringing-disaster-upon-israel/0000018f-82a5-d430-a38f-c7e51d600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，两名泰国人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，他们的尸体被哈马斯扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-two-thai-hostages-were-killed-on-oct-7-their-bodies-held-in-gaza-by-hamas/0000018f-82cb-d720-a79f-abdb31e70000</link><description>两名泰国公民 Sonthaya Oakkharasri 和 Sudthisak Rinthalak 在 Be&amp;#39;eri 基布兹附近的种植园工作，被哈马斯恐怖分子枪杀。军方称哈马斯在加沙扣押的132名人质中有40人被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-says-two-thai-hostages-were-killed-on-oct-7-their-bodies-held-in-gaza-by-hamas/0000018f-82cb-d720-a79f-abdb31e70000</guid></item><item><title>“自 1967 年以来，以色列从未赢得过任何战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ever-since-1967-israel-hasnt-managed-to-win-any-war/0000018f-81ec-d9d6-a38f-85ffd5910000</link><description>双桅船。多夫·塔马里将军（退役）表示，以色列国防机构负责人应该告诉内塔尼亚胡总理，他无权管理加沙战争。在一次采访中，他谈到了秘密突击队核行动，并声称你无法在军事上击败恐怖组织</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:16:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/ever-since-1967-israel-hasnt-managed-to-win-any-war/0000018f-81ec-d9d6-a38f-85ffd5910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙边境附近武器意外爆炸中丧生的士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-soldier-killed-in-accidental-weaponry-explosion-near-gaza-border/0000018f-82b3-d720-a79f-abf3cb1f0000</link><description>中士。兰·亚维茨 (Ran Yavetz) 少校是一天内因行动事故而丧生的第六名以色列士兵，此前，加沙北部有五名士兵因以色列坦克意外开火而丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 19:08:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-soldier-killed-in-accidental-weaponry-explosion-near-gaza-border/0000018f-82b3-d720-a79f-abf3cb1f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心藐视法庭，以色列教育部允许以色列-巴勒斯坦丧亲家庭团体返回学校</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-allows-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-group-to-return-to-schools/0000018f-8276-d430-a38f-c7f66ec60000</link><description>上个月，耶路撒冷地方法院命令以色列政府允许“家长圈-家庭论坛”继续举行学生与以色列和巴勒斯坦死者家属之间的会议，但教育部直到现在才这样做</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:52:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-allows-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-group-to-return-to-schools/0000018f-8276-d430-a38f-c7f66ec60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列真正的问题是内塔尼亚胡和他的极右翼盟友更喜欢哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-16/ty-article/.highlight/israels-real-problem-is-that-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies-prefer-hamas/0000018f-827e-d7f9-a5ff-b77eb8aa0000</link><description>如果内塔尼亚胡如愿以偿，而国防部长加兰特的警告被忽视，哈马斯将再次成为加沙的统治者——为内塔尼亚胡提供他对以色列下次选举的主要承诺：消灭该组织</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 18:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-16/ty-article/.highlight/israels-real-problem-is-that-netanyahu-and-his-far-right-allies-prefer-hamas/0000018f-827e-d7f9-a5ff-b77eb8aa0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列国防部长刚刚对内塔尼亚胡的加沙战争瘫痪打破沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-defense-minister-just-broke-his-silence-about-netanyahus-gaza-war-paralysis/0000018f-81fb-d720-a79f-abfbebf10000</link><description>以色列国防部长加兰特在新闻发布会上呼吁在加沙制定“事后计划”，这是他第三次公开批评内塔尼亚胡。虽然它不会让内塔尼亚胡垮台，但预示着更多的动荡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:33:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/why-israels-defense-minister-just-broke-his-silence-about-netanyahus-gaza-war-paralysis/0000018f-81fb-d720-a79f-abfbebf10000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列心理健康危机的加剧，儿童和青少年精神科医生纷纷离开公共部门</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-crisis-in-israel-grows-child-psychiatrists-leave-public-sector-in-droves/0000018f-81df-d720-a79f-abdf54270000</link><description>议会健康委员会提供的数据显示，尽管自 10 月 7 日以来儿童和青少年的心理健康问题有所增加，但需要心理健康专业人员的青少年可能需要等待八个月或更长时间才能得到治疗</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:17:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/as-mental-health-crisis-in-israel-grows-child-psychiatrists-leave-public-sector-in-droves/0000018f-81df-d720-a79f-abdf54270000</guid></item><item><title>新纳粹好奇心和以色列的捍卫者：侨民部长奇克利前往西班牙极右翼代表大会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/neo-nazi-curious-champions-of-israel-diaspora-minister-heads-to-spains-far-right-confab/0000018f-8192-d7f9-a5ff-b5f6d7fc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府部长阿米哈伊·奇克利 (Amichai Chikli) 称匈牙利的欧尔班·维克多 (Viktor Orban) 为“一位杰出的领导人”，并参加了欧洲各地的一系列极右翼会议。欢迎新纳粹分子和大屠杀否认者加入其队伍</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:17:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/neo-nazi-curious-champions-of-israel-diaspora-minister-heads-to-spains-far-right-confab/0000018f-8192-d7f9-a5ff-b5f6d7fc0000</guid></item><item><title>“让美丽和恐怖发生在我身上：”10 月 7 日的以色列诗歌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/let-beauty-and-terror-happen-to-me-israeli-poems-on-october-7/0000018f-8122-d7f9-a5ff-b57627e60000</link><description>以色列诗人的作品被翻译成英语、法语、意大利语和西班牙语，收录在一本关于 10 月 7 日恐怖事件的新诗集中。另外，一个新的展览“预示”要求艺术家和参与者做到这一点，Etgar Keret出版第七部短篇小说集</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:09:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/let-beauty-and-terror-happen-to-me-israeli-poems-on-october-7/0000018f-8122-d7f9-a5ff-b57627e60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 223 天：阿拉伯联盟呼吁国际部队进驻加沙和约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-223-arab-league-calls-for-international-force-in-gaza-west-bank/0000018f-8234-d7f9-a5ff-b7767c470000</link><description>美国高级官员表示，美国与以色列国防部长加兰特一样担心以色列没有“战后”计划 ■ 加兰特表示，更多部队将加入以色列在拉法的行动 ■ 美国停泊临时浮动码头，向加沙海滩运送援助物资 ■ 以色列国防军正在进行调查以色列国防军坦克在加沙开火导致 5 名士兵死亡 ■ 真主党向以色列发射 40 枚火箭弹和爆炸性无人机 ■ 战争进入 223 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:05:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-223-arab-league-calls-for-international-force-in-gaza-west-bank/0000018f-8234-d7f9-a5ff-b7767c470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵、国防部和军队无意中透露了加沙的部队集中情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-troops-defense-ministry-and-army-unwittingly-reveal-troop-concentrations-in-gaza/0000018f-8203-d7f9-a5ff-b7772dcd0000</link><description>社交媒体上发布的加沙视频显示了确切位置并危及部队。至少一处地方有士兵受伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 17:01:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-troops-defense-ministry-and-army-unwittingly-reveal-troop-concentrations-in-gaza/0000018f-8203-d7f9-a5ff-b7772dcd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在约旦河西岸被刺伤，伤势轻微；以色列国防军逮捕嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-stabbed-in-west-bank-in-moderate-condition-idf-arrests-suspect/0000018f-8228-d430-a38f-c7ec74960000</link><description>该士兵在车内被刺伤，独立抵达附近一个军旅后被送往医院。经过三个小时的搜查，军方宣布在约旦河西岸的阿瓦尔塔村逮捕了一名嫌疑人</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:43:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-stabbed-in-west-bank-in-moderate-condition-idf-arrests-suspect/0000018f-8228-d430-a38f-c7ec74960000</guid></item><item><title>“必须阻止以色列”：南非结束国际法院辩论，呼吁以色列完全撤出加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/israel-must-be-stopped-s-africa-closes-icj-case-calls-for-full-withdrawal-from-gaza/0000018f-820d-dd4f-ab8f-97add0cb0000</link><description>国际法院听证会是在南非上周要求采取额外紧急措施以保护加沙南部拉法之后举行的。该国要求命令人道主义援助提供者不受阻碍地进入加沙，并补充说以色列迄今为止无视法院的命令</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:36:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/israel-must-be-stopped-s-africa-closes-icj-case-calls-for-full-withdrawal-from-gaza/0000018f-820d-dd4f-ab8f-97add0cb0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党火箭弹袭击以色列北部，三名士兵受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/three-soldiers-wounded-as-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-targets-northern-israel/0000018f-81fe-d9d6-a38f-85ff11d10000</link><description>无人机袭击以色列北部的一辆军车后，一名以色列士兵受重伤。真主党表示，这是对以色列对黎巴嫩境内发动的袭击的报复。以色列在黎巴嫩南部发动的袭击造成两人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 16:11:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/three-soldiers-wounded-as-hezbollah-rocket-barrage-targets-northern-israel/0000018f-81fe-d9d6-a38f-85ff11d10000</guid></item><item><title>新星节大屠杀幸存者穿着印有加沙人质肖像的连衣裙出席戛纳电影节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/nova-festival-survivor-attends-cannes-film-festival-wearing-dress-with-hostages-portraits/0000018f-81a1-d7f9-a5ff-b5f7066a0000</link><description>10 月 7 日诺瓦节大屠杀中幸存的劳拉·布莱曼-卡达尔 (Laura Blajman-Kadar) 决定在戛纳红毯上让人们认识到仍在加沙被扣为人质的 132 名以色列人。 “我的裙子上印着我朋友的照片，这让我感到充满力量，我知道我这样做是为了他们”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 14:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-16/ty-article/.premium/nova-festival-survivor-attends-cannes-film-festival-wearing-dress-with-hostages-portraits/0000018f-81a1-d7f9-a5ff-b5f7066a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>